{"tid":2331224,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】TVB 新聞部男主播家人確診　列密切接觸者　消息指曾與同事聚餐","createTime":"2020-12-18T15:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T07:17:53.000Z","uid":212249,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f0b2608cd2f1cc02d82b73a973df045214127365","tid":2331224,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/AfKL8Em5RzE7DO0x_hYv3g_mUbe-Ku9_zxr2KM8a9ig20copy_NYiOl_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FAfKL8Em5RzE7DO0x_hYv3g_mUbe-Ku9_zxr2KM8a9ig20copy_NYiOl_1200x0.png&h=9f01ab61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐，本港亦曾有多間新聞機構有員工確診。《立場新聞》接獲消息，一名 TVB 新聞部男主播的母親初步確診，他亦被列為密切接觸者，消息指，該主播近日曾與其他同事一同聚餐。《無綫電視》回覆《立場》查詢時表示，今日 (18 日）下午 5 時收到新聞及資訊部通知，一名男主播因家人被初步確診武漢肺炎，被列為緊密接觸者。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》及後收到《無綫電視》公關致電，要求將「一名男主播因家人被初步確診武漢肺炎」，改為其新聞稿原稿的「新冠狀病毒病」。<br />\n<br />\n《無綫電視》稱，該員工最後上通宵班至 12 月 14 日早上 7 時，曾與他有接觸的新聞部員工須接受檢測，公司已安排進行消毒清潔，事件並沒有影響新聞部運作。<br />\n<br />\nTVB 在今年第三波疫情時已有員工感染，其中在 8 月時，一名《娛樂新聞台》導演確診，曾回電視城剪片。歌手施匡翹亦在 7 月確診，她曾在潛伏期到過無綫電視城，接觸的藝人、劇組、製作組及台前幕後人員逾百人。"},{"pid":"d31660ee065aeeec360beeedab4fab1d903969ed","tid":2331224,"uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:18:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/武漢肺炎-tvb-新聞部男主播家人確診-列密切接觸者-消息指曾與同事聚餐/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-tvb-%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E9%83%A8%E7%94%B7%E4%B8%BB%E6%92%AD%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%88%97%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E6%8E%A5%E8%A7%B8%E8%80%85-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%9B%BE%E8%88%87%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8B%E8%81%9A%E9%A4%90%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBf8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=5863ee85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-tvb-%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E9%83%A8%E7%94%B7%E4%B8%BB%E6%92%AD%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%88%97%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E6%8E%A5%E8%A7%B8%E8%80%85-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%9B%BE%E8%88%87%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8B%E8%81%9A%E9%A4%90%2F&h=cd98ad52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/武漢肺炎-tvb-新聞部男主播家人確診-列密切接觸者-消息指曾與同事聚餐/</a>"},{"pid":"44193c0a9d9a9712f1e65cbf41c8314908a0215b","tid":2331224,"uid":264426,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:22:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8edf3e394129cf60844efc209faf9b2fcdfaf867","tid":2331224,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:27:19.000Z","msg":"做得tvb就預左架啦 唔抵可憐"},{"pid":"82e6dc25fdeaed63477a544c33665c08b72b90d3","tid":2331224,"uid":138948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:31:07.000Z","msg":"真係恭喜你"},{"pid":"e4dbba2a2da3650e9601dcd579663cd454158979","tid":2331224,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"袁花你保重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4bd86185693eee107d5672a7c305551bca9b8a","tid":2331224,"uid":50327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4dbba2a2da3650e9601dcd579663cd454158979","tid":2331224,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"袁花你保重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:38:25.000Z","msg":"袁花變肺花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f35448ac05385a0af430f718f869a21a3c8527d","tid":2331224,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:44:22.000Z","msg":"我最期待嘅畫面出現啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc15fcbc2fbb0a0833b72d2f1e386ee80d7e404","tid":2331224,"uid":210669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:44:45.000Z","msg":